    <p><span>River City Saga: Journey to the West, Tetris the Grand Master 4: Absolute Eye, etc.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em>A-Ttrain9 Evolution</em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> and <em><a title="Games > Final Fantasy VII Rebirth [32 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth">Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a> and Switch 2 are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1051602"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > River City Saga: Journey to the West [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/river-city-saga-journey-to-the-west">River City Saga: Journey to the West</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, and <em><a title="Games > Tetris the Grand Master 4: Absolute Eye [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tetris-the-grand-master-4-absolute-eye">Tetris the Grand Master 4: Absolute Eye</a></em> for Switch.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > A-Train9 Evolution [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/a-train9-evolution">A-Train9 Evolution</a></em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/a-train9-evolution/13/70jktr?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)<ul><li>40th Anniversary Memorial Box (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/a-train9-evolution-40th-anniversary-memorial-box/13/70jktv?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        </li><li><em>CRAZY CHA!N: Elpis no Kusari</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/crazy-chan-elpis-no-kusari-/13/70j9sz?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)<ul><li>Special Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/crazy-chan-elpis-no-kusari-special-edition/13/70j9tb?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em><a title="Games > eFootball Kick-Off! [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/efootball-kick-off">eFootball Kick-Off!</a></em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/efootball-kick-off-multi-language/13/70jlf3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Game-key card. Launching digitally worldwide.<ul><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/efootball-kick-off-multi-language/13/70jlf7?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em>Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</em> (New Price Version) (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth-new-price-version-multi-language/13/70jlpt?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>)</li><li><em>Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth-multi-language/13/70jlej?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Game-key card. Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth/13/70jl9n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth/13/70jl9p?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth-multi-language/13/70jlel?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em><a title="Games > John Carpenter's Toxic Commando [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/john-carpenters-toxic-commando">John Carpenter’s Toxic Commando</a></em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/john-carpenters-toxic-commando/13/70g8of?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Already available worldwide.</li><li><em>The Last Case of John Morley</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-last-case-of-john-morley-multi-language/13/70jmyp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Already available worldwide.<ul><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-last-case-of-john-morley-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jmyt?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>)</li></ul></li></ul><h2><span>Digital-Only</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > The 7th Guest Remake [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-7th-guest-remake">The 7th Guest Remake</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4491360/The_7th_Guest_Remake/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/the-7th-guest-remake-28882c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Beholder: Conductor [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/beholder-conductor">Beholder: Conductor</a></em> (PS5, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > BrokenLore: FOLLOW [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/brokenlore-follow">BrokenLore: FOLLOW</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2846530/BrokenLore_FOLLOW/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Final Fantasy VII Rebirth</em> (Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth/9n4728d0t6jn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Game-key card. Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > GOALS" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/goals">GOALS</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2753000/GOALS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Gothic</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1297900/Gothic_1_Remake/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://www.gog.com/en/game/gothic_1_remake" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GOG</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Hollowbody [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/hollowbody">Hollowbody</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > House Flipper Remastered Collection [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/house-flipper-remastered-collection">House Flipper Remastered Collection</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3710840/House_Flipper_Remastered_Collection/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Isekai Villain</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PS4, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4340820/Isekai_Villain/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/isekai-villain/9NNXQKNKN168" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Platforms > N64" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/n64">Nintendo 64</a> – <a title="Platforms > Nintendo [23,696 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> Classics</em> (Switch 2, Switch)<ul><li><em>Donkey Kong 64</em> – Launching worldwide.</li></ul></li><li><em>River City Saga: Journey to the West</em> (PS5, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4164020/River_City_Saga_Journey_to_the_West/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>The Sinking Forest</em> (Xbox Series, Xbox One, PC [<a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/the-sinking-forest-%E6%B2%88%E3%82%93%E3%81%A0%E6%A3%AE/9P0FKV1VGQQ4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Steamboat Incident</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2822620/Steamboat_Incident/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Tetris the Grand Master 4: Absolute Eye</em> (Switch)</li></ul><p>The PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and Switch titles listed above can be purchased through Japanese <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [49,687 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> Network and Nintendo accounts using prepaid cards:</p><ul><li>PlayStation Store cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-1100-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/70dc0b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,100</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-3000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/%20-card-5000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk4?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-10000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10,000</a></li><li>Nintendo eShop cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1500-yen-japan-account/13/70cte9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,500</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-3000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2w?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-5000-yen-japan-account/13/705239?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-9000-yen-japan-account/13/70bkw5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9,000</a></li></ul><p>Additionally, direct top-ups for gacha games are available <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/14/7133p?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>, including:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/blue_protocol:_star_resonance/14/713bp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blue Protocol: Star Resonance</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/genshin_impact/14/7133t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Genshin Impact</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/honkai_star_rail/14/7133z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Honkai: Star Rail</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Love and Deepspace</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/marvel_rivals/14/7134t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Marvel Rivals</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Where Winds Meet</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/zenless_zone_zero/14/7134z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Zenless Zone Zero</em></a></li></ul><h2><span>Demos, DLC, Updates, etc.</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > Arknights: Endfield [16 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/arknights-endfield">Arknights: Endfield</a></em> 